testcase.name: testAccessibility

failure.message:
Accessibility issues found: Found 5 accessibility violations: 1) Text of buttons and links should not be repeated in the image alternative: https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/3.1/image-redundant-alt?application=axeAPI a) ["a[aria-label=\"Headsets\"]"] Fix all of the following: Element contains <img> element with alt text that duplicates existing text
b) ["a[aria-label=\"Keyboards\"]"] Fix all of the following: Element contains <img> element with alt text that duplicates existing text
c) ["a[aria-label=\"Computer\\ mice\"]"] Fix all of the following: Element contains <img> element with alt text that duplicates existing text
d) ["a[aria-label=\"Chairs\"]"] Fix all of the following: Element contains <img> element with alt text that duplicates existing text
e) ["a[aria-label=\"Dining\"]"] Fix all of the following: Element contains <img> element with alt text that duplicates existing text
f) ["a[aria-label=\"Home\"]"] Fix all of the following: Element contains <img> element with alt text that duplicates existing text
g) ["a[aria-label=\"Kitchen\"]"] Fix all of the following: Element contains <img> element with alt text that duplicates existing text
h) ["a[aria-label=\"Health\\ and\\ Beauty\"]"] Fix all of the following: Element contains <img> element with alt text that duplicates existing text
i) ["a[aria-label=\"Dresses\"]"] Fix all of the following: Element contains <img> element with alt text that duplicates existing text
j) ["a[aria-label=\"Knits\"]"] Fix all of the following: Element contains <img> element with alt text that duplicates existing text
k) ["a[aria-label=\"Jackets\"]"] Fix all of the following: Element contains <img> element with alt text that duplicates existing text
l) ["a[aria-label=\"Jewelry\"]"] Fix all of the following: Element contains <img> element with alt text that duplicates existing text
2) Form elements should have a visible label: https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/3.1/label-title-only?application=axeAPI a) ["#searchDropdownBox"] Fix all of the following: Only title used to generate label for form element
3) Form elements must have labels: https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/3.1/label?application=axeAPI a) ["#searchDropdownBox"] Fix all of the following: Form element has explicit <label> that is hidden
b) ["#twotabsearchtextbox"] Fix all of the following: Form element has explicit <label> that is hidden
4) Page must contain a level-one heading: https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/3.1/page-has-heading-one?application=axeAPI a) ["html"] Fix all of the following: Page must have a level-one heading
5) All page content must be contained by landmarks: https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/3.1/region?application=axeAPI a) ["html"] Fix any of the following: Some page content is not contained by landmarks
